codeText: public static DeweyNumber fromString(final String deweyNumberString) {_		String[] splits = deweyNumberString.split("\\.")___		if (splits.length == 0) {_			return new DeweyNumber(Integer.parseInt(deweyNumberString))__		} else {_			int[] deweyNumber = new int[splits.length]___			for (int i = 0_ i < splits.length_ i++) {_				deweyNumber[i] = Integer.parseInt(splits[i])__			}__			return new DeweyNumber(deweyNumber)__		}_	}
